sentences.english: No one could account for the fact that one of the boxes was extremely heavy.
sentences.chinese: 此中有隻箱子特別重，可誰也弄不清是怎麼回事。

sentences.english: But the meaning of other symbols is not so clear, even to me.
sentences.chinese: 但是其他的符號就不太明顯，甚至我自己也弄不清。

sentences.english: Daughter side, looked at his father's doubts about the his intention.
sentences.chinese: 女兒站在一邊，疑惑地望着父親，弄不清他的用意。

sentences.english: We were wondering whether to go today or tomorrow.
sentences.chinese: 我們弄不清是今天走還是明天走。

sentences.english: Sometimes you just can't tell exactly what is going to work.
sentences.chinese: 有時候，你會弄不清究竟什麼才能成功。

sentences.english: It was moving down the beach toward the water.
sentences.chinese: 他們弄不清這是什麼動物。

sentences.english: I cannot sense your meaning sometimes.
sentences.chinese: 我有時候也弄不清你的用意。

sentences.english: He couldn't tell if she was laughing or crying.
sentences.chinese: 他弄不清她是笑還是哭。
